commitResults.messageTitle: add Task class; mark, unmark functionality for task
update access modifier from private to public for getStatusIcon() function
add 3 classes - Deadline, Event and ToDo which extend the Task class
add logic in Duke.java to handle creation of the 3 different kinds of tasks, ToDo, Event and Deadline
add delete logic and refactored mark and unmark logic
refactor code to split the command at the very beginning when the command is read

commitResults.messageBody:
This commit will add FileManager class so as to handle the read, create and writing functionality of the file.

It has also made some minor modifications to the Task, ToDo, Deadline and Event class, adding the toFileString()
method, which prints out the data in a format to be stored in the .txt file.

The Duke class has also been modified to incorporate the writeToFile functionality whenever there are changes.
Modify Deadline and Event class to now accept dateTime as String and store it as a LocalDate.

Add AddCommand, DeleteCommand, ExitCommand, InvalidCommand, ListCommand, MarkCommand that all extend the Command class.

Add Parser, Storage, TaskList, Ui classes.

Refactored most of the code to make it more OOP

Add minor bug fix which fixes.

Refactor code to package java classes into their own respective packages.
